titleStmt.title: A copy of a paper concerning three propositions presented by the commissioners to the Kings Majesty on Munday last, October 9. 1648. With His Majesties finall answer, returned on Wednesday the 11 of October, concerning Ireland. And His Majesties Propositions for the nomination of a deputy and other officers for 20 years. Presented to the Parliament this present Friday, Octob. 13. 1648. This is a true copy examined. And His Majesties paper, subscribed Charles Rex.
